# API Contract

This document defines all REST API endpoints exposed by JavasinoWeb. All endpoints are prefixed with `/api/v1/`.

---

## Authentication & Users

### Auth
| Method | Endpoint | Auth Required | Description |
|--------|----------|---------------|-------------|
| `POST` | `/api/v1/auth/register` | No | Register a new user |
| `POST` | `/api/v1/auth/login` | No | Login, returns JWT token |

**POST /auth/register — Request body:**
```json
{
  "username": "johndoe",
  "email": "john@example.com",
  "password": "securepassword"
}
```

**POST /auth/login — Request body:**
```json
{
  "email": "john@example.com",
  "password": "securepassword"
}
```

**POST /auth/login — Response:**
```json
{
  "token": "eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9...",
  "username": "johndoe"
}
```

---

### Users
| Method | Endpoint | Auth Required | Description |
|--------|----------|---------------|-------------|
| `GET` | `/api/v1/users/me` | Yes | Get authenticated user profile |
| `PUT` | `/api/v1/users/me` | Yes | Update user profile |

