## Wallet

| Method | Endpoint | Auth Required | Description |
|--------|----------|---------------|-------------|
| `GET` | `/api/v1/wallet/me` | Yes | Get current balance |
| `POST` | `/api/v1/wallet/deposit` | Yes | Deposit credits |
| `POST` | `/api/v1/wallet/withdraw` | Yes | Withdraw credits |
| `GET` | `/api/v1/wallet/transactions` | Yes | Paginated transaction history |
| `GET` | `/api/v1/wallet/transactions/{gameType}` | Yes | Paginated history filtered by game |

**POST /wallet/deposit — Request body:**
```json
{
  "amount": 500
}
```

**GET /wallet/transactions — Response:**
```json
{
  "content": [
    {
      "id": "uuid",
      "amount": 500,
      "type": "DEPOSIT",
      "gameType": "NONE",
      "createdAt": "2026-05-23T10:00:00Z"
    }
  ],
  "page": 0,
  "totalPages": 5,
  "totalElements": 98
}
```

