## Games

### Blackjack

| Method | Endpoint | Auth Required | Description |
|--------|----------|---------------|-------------|
| `POST` | `/api/v1/games/blackjack/start` | Yes | Start session, deal initial cards |
| `POST` | `/api/v1/games/blackjack/hit` | Yes | Player requests a card |
| `POST` | `/api/v1/games/blackjack/stand` | Yes | Player stands, dealer plays |
| `POST` | `/api/v1/games/blackjack/double` | Yes | Double bet, receive one final card |
| `GET` | `/api/v1/games/blackjack/history` | Yes | Paginated session history |

**POST /blackjack/start — Request body:**
```json
{
  "betAmount": 100
}
```

**POST /blackjack/start — Response:**
```json
{
  "sessionId": "uuid",
  "playerCards": ["AS", "KH"],
  "dealerCards": ["7D", "?"],
  "playerScore": 21,
  "status": "IN_PROGRESS"
}
```

**POST /blackjack/hit — Request body:**
```json
{
  "sessionId": "uuid"
}
```

**POST /blackjack/stand — Response:**
```json
{
  "sessionId": "uuid",
  "playerCards": ["AS", "KH"],
  "dealerCards": ["7D", "9C"],
  "playerScore": 21,
  "dealerScore": 16,
  "result": "WIN",
  "payout": 200,
  "status": "FINISHED"
}
```

